{"tid":1820843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再大大聲話香港幫蔡英文贏喇","createTime":"2020-01-11T18:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T02:50:28.000Z","uid":81562,"like":34,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0b6cc56405c06421a3f9b76c00f5b873834c627b","tid":1820843,"uid":81562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:43:49.000Z","msg":"香港牌好重要係真嘅，但人地任內唔係冇政績，能源政策、年金改革、潛艦國造、台美關係、婚姻平權、減稅、長照等等，台灣人自己有眼睇，只係前兩任行政院長廢，先令民眾感受唔到政府做咗乜，換咗蘇貞昌後已經將民望逐步收復。<br />\n<br />\n香港形勢無疑係一大助攻，但大家都要尊重台灣人本身智慧，BE HUMBLE！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acd7770f9de37ecfec55e8b8266cec8f7bd5842","tid":1820843,"uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:45:57.000Z","msg":"唔係香港人幫蔡英文贏<br />\n係韓國瑜自己表現不濟<br />\n<br />\n陳雲話鋒一轉談到許多人認為蔡英文在反送中「撿到槍」，但他認為是韓國瑜自己把槍丟了，蔡英文所做的是執政者的標準做法，支持香港的人權運動、香港民主，以提供香港人必要的救助。但他說，韓國瑜好像「發夢」一樣，「共產黨這麼信他，他一點反對的話也不敢講」，是韓國瑜自己出了問題，不是蔡英文做了甚麼傑出的表現。"},{"pid":"474677ef49f5f94773b87cfc17f83310539db8a6","tid":1820843,"uid":52676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b6cc56405c06421a3f9b76c00f5b873834c627b","tid":1820843,"uid":81562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:43:49.000Z","msg":"香港牌好重要係真嘅，但人地任內唔係冇政績，能源政策、年金改革、潛艦國造、台美關係、婚姻平權、減稅、長照等等，台灣人自己有眼睇，只係前兩任行政院長廢，先令民眾感受唔到政府做咗乜，換咗蘇貞昌後已經將民望逐步收復。<br />\n<br />\n香港形勢無疑係一大助攻，但大家都要尊重台灣人本身智慧，BE HUMBLE！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:46:50.000Z","msg":"岩呀，要尊重返台灣"},{"pid":"f16c12c8307e009802f6359c693c7cb9cce8e247","tid":1820843,"uid":90180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"某位香港人唔好咁功利同自大，<br />\n抹煞民進黨貫徹始終去反共，<br />\n先係勝選最大關鍵。"},{"pid":"b79a0118d94bd7b4e0e45929cdb30963b5994c01","tid":1820843,"uid":109462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:54:17.000Z","msg":"蘋果訪問中研院副研究員、親綠學者吳叡人<br />\n<br />\n//台灣即將舉行大選，吳認為民進黨蔡英文能成功連任，「香港人救了蔡英文，救了本土政權」，指香港根本性地改變台灣社會意識發展的方向，「亡國感擴散到每個人」。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200104/60447090?fbclid=IwAR2ZM-s0r3VWWOfNGhX7iiPzva7lk6tojAV_rYzx0RQQzpzLC0AaCKkpkY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F60447090%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2ZM-s0r3VWWOfNGhX7iiPzva7lk6tojAV_rYzx0RQQzpzLC0AaCKkpkY4&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=3af85733\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F60447090%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2ZM-s0r3VWWOfNGhX7iiPzva7lk6tojAV_rYzx0RQQzpzLC0AaCKkpkY4&h=c8fc91c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200104/60447090?fbclid=IwAR2ZM-s0r3VWWOfNGhX7iiPzva7lk6tojAV_rYzx0RQQzpzLC0AaCKkpkY4</a>"},{"pid":"b0bbd076c004bca771f1572fb6db5997582dc94d","tid":1820843,"uid":288670,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:57:59.000Z","msg":"事實黎 點解唔講得"},{"pid":"2aea52c3d8b948ab722c7e6cb8152309bb219192","tid":1820843,"uid":81562,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0bbd076c004bca771f1572fb6db5997582dc94d","tid":1820843,"uid":288670,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:57:59.000Z","msg":"事實黎 點解唔講得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07259ed772cdb12704126dfbad9dfe95d08a9e03","tid":1820843,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"根本蔡英文由2012年起開始選就有6,000,000選票<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4227573dc03cd04cbb85492cb847a450bbe1b2","ti